{center}
{subhead}Freespace demo update 4 released{def}
{left}
{pp}
The fourth update  of the game demo of Freespace has been released
for download on the Hyperion homepage. It removes several smaller bugs as well as a 
new option to allow switching voicestreaming on and off.
{pp}
Also included is a description how you have to connect an analog joystick.
{pp}